---
title: Chicken Tikka Sammies with Indian-Spiced Wedges and Yogurt Sauce
description: We're serving up all the things you love about chicken tikka stuffed between fluffy buns! Grab a napkin, it's about to get saucy! No sandwich is complete without a delicious side, so we've added crispy spiced wedges and a creamy yogurt dip for good measure.
